Package: scamtracker
Type: Package
Title: Tools to Work with the 'Better Business Bureau' Scam Tracker
Version: 0.2.0
Date: 2017-04-03
Author: Bob Rudis (@hrbrmstr)
Maintainer: Bob Rudis <bob@rud.is>
Description: The 'Better Business Bureau' provides a public 'API' which lets consumers
    and businesses report and monitor active and past "scams". Tools are provided to query
    the service.
